slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"玩左幾次。<br />\n唔知係咪太自由，定任務太散，每次都堅持唔到"},{"pid":"80648b36cfafaf504370b53880aebcceae47183d","tid":1311329,"uid":12889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:21:24.000Z","msg":"萬年新手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次一開game都冇乜心機打，一來地圖太大，二來錬金game入面冇recipe, 次次執到成身都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：有pc版+switch版，想儲埋ps4版"},{"pid":"76701d9901a49f7a45a38f5810d019c8f96cc165","tid":1311329,"uid":172889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:49:27.000Z","msg":"次次都想玩大加近戰build<br />\n點知次次玩玩下都變咗射箭隱身法師嗰類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771a836482b6c19c40c022c03cb051eb9b3dc8aa","tid":1311329,"uid":50561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"最無腦一定係隱身弓箭手build<br />\n由1至75等都可以免費升<br />\n1至50係riverwoid幫faendal,之後收佢做follower,搵佢train然後trade番所有錢俾自己<br />\n50lv後清companion條quest line,收aela做follower再train上75，之後去搵書/trainer上80 archery<br />\n平時升多d sneak, Sneak 50拎到sneak弓傷3倍<br />\n80等archery 弓傷2倍<br />\nDawnguard DLC 把enhances dwarven crossbow 本身可以無視50%甲，再加個Dragonborn dlc 嘅chaos damage+fiery soul trap，然後配埋black star可以有無限charge附魔<br />\n甲就要拎ancient shrouded cowl，加35%弓傷<br />\n戒指同頸都用加extreme archery附魔，再多32-35%傷<br />\n基本上可以一嘢秒9成怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681335f1957d2e6c8575ca5b76f8155eed089c5f","tid":1311329,"uid":116625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b3443e67d96d7f0abbb6e0b398f7c6323e62b2f","tid":1311329,"uid":213475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T21:43:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=2526&amp;snA=43610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D2526%26snA%3D43610&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWTbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBI